         <abstract id="aspace_4d9edd225c000c00f8468ccd277f97d2">The motion picture film depicts Yale building sites and construction. Buildings documented include South Sheffield, gymnasium, Sloane Laboratory, Divinity School, Park Street dormitories, Graduate School, Law School, Sterling Memorial Library, Forestry School, Branford Court, and Harkness Tower.</abstract>
    
